NOT MEDICAL ADVICE. TriageIQ is an emergency-department decision-support
demonstration. It is not clinically validated, has not been compared against
trained-nurse ESI ground truth on a held-out patient set, and must not be used
to triage real patients without institutional review (IRB), a defined
decision-support framework agreed with medical staff, malpractice coverage that
contemplates AI-assisted decision support, and an EHR integration with the
required privacy controls. All patient records, vitals, chief complaints, and
clinical protocols in this repository are fabricated for demonstration. No
real patient, medical institution, or clinical relationship is represented.
